name: The Giant Busy Board
description:
Interactive Busy Board for your toddler! Keep em busy with this for hours:) 


The Busy Board is built of birch plywood. Paint is water based, easy to wipe clean!
Our Boards come with four screws, ready to be hung on your wall! 

We offer two different size busy boards. 

The Giant Board 24inx18in

We offer 4 different colors!! Due to different computer screens, it is very hard to match colors. In order to get an exact color, you must do a custom order. any color is possible! Please convo us for custom color information!
